## Client side settings

# More commonly changed settings
BatchMode yes 
# ^optimistically set as "yes" for the future, but practically may be "no" until it's confirmed that all common workflows don't require prompting
StrictHostKeyChecking yes

# Settings for specific session use cases; set to deny by default, but reasonable to override
